name: BinauralBeats
0:
”Alexa open binaural beats”
”Alexa ask binaural beats to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: binaural beats
des:
Enhance focus with Binaural Beats! Drive your deep focus sessions with these science backed 40hz binaural beats. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Binaural Beats, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
